questions.questionText:
What does this CSS produce?

```css
.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  grid-template-rows: 100px 200px;
  gap: 12px;
}
/* items: a, b, c, d, e, f */
```

What is the resulting width of each column?

```css
.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr 2fr;
  width: 1000px;
  gap: 0px;
}
```
